{"tid":49421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[報應來了]馬路如虎口！「反辱華」大會後遇車禍　","createTime":"2016-12-21T16:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T03:28:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e58193699bafffd8759ae82a2bcbf3f7df519f2a","tid":49421,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161121/s00001/1479724718825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161121%2Fs00001%2F1479724718825&d=MbehmNRN3VdOyAzoHD%2FQAZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=53ca2028\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161121%2Fs00001%2F1479724718825&h=a256513c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161121/s00001/1479724718825</a><br />\n<br />\n城大專業進修學院市場營銷管理學一年級生莫嘉傑，最近因在網上發起聯署，收集逾60萬簽名反青政梁、游兩人，又就劉小麗等宣誓申請司法覆核，頻頻曝光於傳媒鏡頭下。不過Emily見到佢今日到旺角法律援助署申請法援嗰陣，要靠拐杖出行，點解嘅點解嘅？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來佢上個月尾出席完喺立法會外搞嘅「反辱華反港獨」集會後，離開現場時竟遇到車禍，搞到右腳膝蓋十字韌帶斷裂，嚴重到要瞓幾日醫院呀！Emily見到，佢左手上面仲有一大片紫色瘀痕，真係睇到都痛。<br />\n<br />\n莫嘉傑透露，依家等緊排期，要動手術處理傷勢。不過發生咁大件事，都無阻佢繼續發起反梁、游及劉小麗嘅多個行動，包括申請司法覆核，帶傷上陣，意志搭夠。點都好，Emily希望佢多啲休息，早日康復啦！"},{"pid":"c8231d1a72d6e3a66b46f2064be3311f87a25583","tid":49421,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb6b671a761dbc9a625c32b31ef73a3b02ee5e14","tid":49421,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f2b1559368af0fec2b87b8052f6ce6f18638c5","tid":49421,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"機界五毛你洗撚完版未？<br />\n做回帶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80